'''Dailon Rocha Livramento do Rosario''' ({{IPA|pt|ˈdaj.lɔn ˈʀɔ.ʃɐ li.vɾɐ.ˈmẽ.tu du ʀu.ˈza.ɾi.u|lang}}; born 4 May 2001) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Primeira Liga]] club [[Casa Pia A.C.|Casa Pia]], on loan from [[Serie A]] club [[Hellas Verona FC|Hellas Verona]]. Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].<ref name="mvv" /><ref>{{GSA player|dailon-livramento/7732314}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Roda JC===
Livramento was born in [[Rotterdam]], and played youth football for [[Excelsior Rotterdam|Excelsior]], Sparta AV, [[Excelsior Maassluis]], and [[NAC Breda]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Dailon Livramento: Dé man in vorm bij NAC O-19 |url=https://www.bsiderats.nl/nieuws/dailon-livramento-de-man-in-vorm-bij-nac-o-19 |access-date=17 February 2023 |work=Bsiderats |date=15 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210921142841/https://www.bsiderats.nl/nieuws/dailon-livramento-de-man-in-vorm-bij-nac-o-19 |archive-date=21 September 2021 |language=nl}}</ref> In 2021, he moved to [[Roda JC Kerkrade]], where he initially joined the under-21 team. He made his professional debut for the first team on 26 October 2021, starting in a 2–1 win over [[FC Den Bosch]] in the [[KNVB Cup]] in which he contributed with his first goal.<ref>{{cite news |last1=Leenders |first1=Jimmy |title=Debutant Livramento bij Roda: na mijn doelpunt moest ik bijna huilen |url=https://www.limburger.nl/cnt/dmf20211026_97863852 |access-date=17 February 2023 |work=De Limburger |date=26 October 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215173814/https://www.limburger.nl/cnt/dmf20211026_97863852 |archive-date=15 February 2022 |language=nl}}</ref>

===MVV===
On 3 August 2022, Livramento signed a two-year contract with an option for an additional year with [[Eerste Divisie]] club [[MVV Maastricht|MVV]].<ref name="mvv">{{cite web |title=Livramento tekent contract van 2+1 |url=https://www.mvv.nl/nieuws/livramento-tekent-contract-van-2-1 |website=MVV |access-date=17 February 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220818140951/https://www.mvv.nl/nieuws/livramento-tekent-contract-van-2-1 |archive-date=18 August 2022 |language=NL |date=3 August 2022}}</ref> He made his debut for the club on the first matchday of the [[2022–23 Eerste Divisie|2022–23 season]], replacing [[Thomas van Bommel]] in the 74th minute of a 3–1 loss to [[Jong AZ]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Puts |first1=Wim |title=Valse start voor MVV: 3-1 nederlaag tegen Jong AZ |url=https://www.1limburg.nl/sport/1820739/valse-start-voor-mvv-3-1-nederlaag-tegen-jong-az |access-date=25 January 2023 |work=1limburg |date=8 August 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221006014819/https://www.1limburg.nl/sport/1820739/valse-start-voor-mvv-3-1-nederlaag-tegen-jong-az |archive-date=6 October 2022 |language=nl}}</ref> On 19 August, he scored his first professional goal as well as his first goal for the club, bagging the last goal of a 3–1 home win over [[ADO Den Haag]].<ref>{{cite web |title=ADO Den Haag verliest met 3–1 in Maastricht |url=https://adodenhaag.nl/nl/teams/1e-elftal/resultaten/931-mvv-maastricht-ado-den-haag-931 |website=ADO Den Haag |access-date=15 January 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221030180057/https://adodenhaag.nl/nl/teams/1e-elftal/resultaten/931-mvv-maastricht-ado-den-haag-931 |archive-date=30 October 2022 |language=nl |date=19 August 2022 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=MVV – ADO Den Haag 3:1 (Eerste Divisie 2022/2023, 3. Round) |url=https://www.worldfootball.net/match-report/ma9415673/lineup/ |website=WorldFootball.net |publisher=HEIM:SPIEL |access-date=15 January 2023}}</ref>

Livramento established himself as a starter for MVV in the second half of the [[2023–24 Eerste Divisie|2023–24 season]] and proved to be a productive goalscorer.<ref>{{cite news |title=Dailon Livramento en Ferre Slegers lijken de leegte van Koen Kostons te vullen bij MVV |url=https://keukenkampioendivisie.nl/nieuws/dailon-livramento-en-ferre-slegers-lijken-de-leegte-van-koen-kostons-te-vullen-bij-mvv |access-date=9 June 2024 |work=Keuken Kampioen Divisie |date=18 January 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240609083952/https://keukenkampioendivisie.nl/nieuws/dailon-livramento-en-ferre-slegers-lijken-de-leegte-van-koen-kostons-te-vullen-bij-mvv |archive-date=9 June 2024 |language=nl}}</ref> He finished the season with 16 goals in 36 appearances, as MVV finished ninth, narrowly missing out on promotion play-offs by goal difference.<ref name="SW" /><ref>{{cite news |last1=Appeven |first1=Stephan van |title=MVV loopt ondanks probleemloze zege play-offs mis |url=https://rtvmaastricht.nl/nieuws/artikel/mvv-loopt-ondanks-probleemloze-zege-play-offs-mis |access-date=9 June 2024 |work=RTV Maastricht |date=10 May 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240609084413/https://rtvmaastricht.nl/nieuws/artikel/mvv-loopt-ondanks-probleemloze-zege-play-offs-mis |archive-date=9 June 2024 |language=nl}}</ref>

===Hellas Verona===
On 24 July 2024, Livramento signed a four-year contract with [[Serie A]] club [[Hellas Verona FC|Hellas Verona]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Dailon Rocha Livramento is a new Yellow-Blue striker! |url=https://www.hellasverona.it/en/news/dailon-rocha-livramento-is-a-new-yellow-blue-striker |website=Hellas Verona FC |access-date=24 July 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240724135204/https://www.hellasverona.it/en/news/dailon-rocha-livramento-is-a-new-yellow-blue-striker |archive-date=24 July 2024 |date=24 July 2024}}</ref> He made his debut for the club on 10 August, coming on as a substitute for [[Abdou Harroui]] in the 55th minute of a disappointing 2–1 [[Coppa Italia]] loss to [[Cesena FC|Cesena]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Hellas Verona 1–2 Cesena |url=https://www.legaseriea.it/en/media/coppa-italia/hellas-verona-1-2-cesena-13mk7ll5mad9bi |website=Lega Serie A |access-date=25 August 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240825082053/https://www.legaseriea.it/en/media/coppa-italia/hellas-verona-1-2-cesena-13mk7ll5mad9bi |archive-date=25 August 2024 |date=10 August 2024}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Fontana |first1=Matteo |title=Coppa Italia, Verona-Cesena 1–2: l'Hellas ko al Bentegodi finisce fuori |url=https://corrieredelveneto.corriere.it/notizie/verona/sport/24_agosto_10/coppa-italia-verona-cesena-1-2-l-hellas-ko-al-bentegodi-finisce-fuori-daf3b0b5-f164-4b0c-8d37-03e10ea0fxlk.shtml |access-date=25 August 2024 |work=Corriere della Sera |date=10 August 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240811085741/https://corrieredelveneto.corriere.it/notizie/verona/sport/24_agosto_10/coppa-italia-verona-cesena-1-2-l-hellas-ko-al-bentegodi-finisce-fuori-daf3b0b5-f164-4b0c-8d37-03e10ea0fxlk.shtml |archive-date=11 August 2024 |language=it-IT}}</ref> On 18 August, he was included in manager [[Paolo Zanetti]]'s starting lineup for the first matchday of the [[2024–25 Serie A]], where he scored Verona's opening goal of the campaign in a 3–0 victory against [[SSC Napoli|Napoli]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fortino |first1=Samuele |title=Hellas Verona-Napoli 3-0, pagelle: Duda e Daniel Mosquera sontuosi, partenopei bocciati in blocco |url=https://www.eurosport.it/calcio/serie-a/2024-2025/hellas-verona-napoli-3-0-pagelle-duda-e-daniel-mosquera-sontuosi-partenopei-bocciati-in-blocco_sto10305496/story.shtml |access-date=25 August 2024 |work=Eurosport |date=18 August 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240820163203/https://www.eurosport.it/calcio/serie-a/2024-2025/hellas-verona-napoli-3-0-pagelle-duda-e-daniel-mosquera-sontuosi-partenopei-bocciati-in-blocco_sto10305496/story.shtml |archive-date=20 August 2024 |language=it}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Azzi |first1=Marco |title=Verona-Napoli 3-0: la prima di Conte in azzurro è da incubo |url=https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2024/08/18/news/verona_napoli_gol_risultato-423452185/ |access-date=25 August 2024 |work=la Repubblica |date=18 August 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240821110132/https://www.repubblica.it/sport/calcio/serie-a/2024/08/18/news/verona_napoli_gol_risultato-423452185/ |archive-date=21 August 2024 |language=it}}</ref>

On 1 September 2025, Livramento was loaned to [[Casa Pia A.C.|Casa Pia]] in Portugal.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Hellas Verona|url=https://www.hellasverona.it/en/news/dailon-livramento-on-loan-to-casa-pia|title=Dailon Livramento on loan to Casa Pia|date=1 September 2025|access-date=9 September 2025}}</ref>

==International career==
In March 2024, Livramento was called up to the [[Cape Verde national football team|Cape Verde national team]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.l1nieuws.nl/sport/2595227/livramentos-droom-van-mvv-naar-nationaal-team-kaapverdie|title=Livramento's droom: van MVV naar nationaal team Kaapverdië|date=14 March 2024 }}</ref>

